About Us

We are a group of college students driven to solve a problem we've noticed in our communities: Recycling. Recycling is essential to a sustainable future, but we have observed challenges to recycling that make it hard for people to participate. Confusion on varying recycling rules as well as lack of knowledge on where to deposit recyclable items can discourage people from contributing. That's why we have made King County recycling information available in this singular platform.
